title: A proper newe ballad declaring the substaunce of all the late pretended treasons against the Queenes Maiestie, and estates of this realme by sundry traytors who were executed in Lincolnes-Inne fielde on the 20 and 21 daies of September, 1586 : to Wilsons new tune.
author: Nelson, Thomas, fl. 1580.
publisher: By Thomas Purfoote for Edward White,
